      "text": [
        " : «كُلَّمَا أَصَابَ اَلْعَبْدُ اَلْمُحْرِمُ فِي إِحْرَامِهِ فَهُوَ عَلَى اَلسَّيِّدِ إِذَا أَذِنَ لَهُ فِي اَلْإِحْرَامِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2886 - Hariz narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Whatever a servant in the state of Ihram incurs during their Ihram is the responsibility of the master if the master gave permission for the Ihram.\""
